ARTICLE XIV — OFFICERS
ARTICLE XV — INDEMNIFICATION
ARTICLE XVI — DIVIDEND PAYMENTS
ARTICLE XVII — FUNDS AND ACCOUNTING
ARTICLE XVIII — SOVEREIGN IMMUNITY
ARTICLE XIX — AMENDMENTS
